WelcomePROFOX Associates, Inc. – Providing expertise in medical software since 1987.   Our advanced software solutions support a wide range of medical devices and environments, including customized software to meet the growing needs of a rapidly changing industry.
How can we help you today?


SoftwareLooking for a solution for your sleep apnea and oxygen presciption studies?  PROFOX oximeter downloading software works with a wide variety of pulse oximeters and capnographs.View software products

SupportNeed help installing or configuring one of our software products?  A technical support specialist is standing by to assist you via phone or Email, Monday through Friday, 8am - 4pm Pacific Standard Time.Contact Support

SalesDo you have questions about pricing?  Are you looking for discounts when purchasing multiple copies of a product at once?  Are you a re-seller?  Do you have a feature request?  We would be glad to discuss our various pricing options with you.Contact Sales

DevelopmentAre you a manufacturer looking for a highly skilled and industry-proven software development team to help bring your device to market?  Do you have questions about adding customized features to an existing product?Read MoreAbout usPROFOX Associates, Inc. was founded in 1987 out of a desire to improve patient care through accurately reporting patient test data in ways that are easy to understand.  This allowed physicians to quickly find the information they needed in order to properly diagnose health conditions. 
More About UsBreathe Easier with industry standard software from PROFOXIndustry Standard ReportingPROFOX’s copyrighted reports are  easy to read, easy to interpret, and include all of the information you expect from the industry’s preferred oximetry software.  You can print in color or gray-scale, or you can fax directly from the computer.  All reports have wide left margins to accommodate chart-folds and use large character sizes so the reports can be easily read after being copied or sent via fax.
